      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey everyone! I'm parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, this car is a total dream. It\u2019s in gorgeous, showroom-level condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just left the dealership! I\u2019ve been super meticulous about keeping it spotless and well-loved, so it's ready for its next adventure with zero worries. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically perfect and drives like a cloud, this is the one! Shoot me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
