    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a definitive example of the E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a flawless Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission. This vehicle has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance: the VANOS system has been overhauled with upgraded seals, and the rod bearings have been replaced to ensure long-term reciprocating assembly health. The rear subframe has been reinforced to mitigate common chassis fatigue, maintaining factory-spec torsional rigidity. Performance is further sharpened by a mechanical limited-slip differential and refreshed suspension geometry with high-durometer bushings. The exterior finish remains impeccable with consistent paint depth readings, and the undercarriage is free of fluid seepage or oxidative stress.",
